Ext.data.JsonP['Titanium_Blob']({"tagname":"class","name":"Titanium.Blob","extends":"Titanium.Proxy","mixins":[],"alternateClassNames":[],"aliases":{},"singleton":false,"requires":[],"uses":[],"enum":null,"override":null,"inheritable":null,"inheritdoc":null,"meta":{"platform":["android 0.9","iphone 0.9","ipad 0.9","windowsphone 4.1.0"],"editurl":"https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/edit/master/apidoc/Titanium/Blob.yml","description":["<p>A <code>Blob</code> represents a chunk of binary information, often obtained through\nan {@link Titanium.Network.HTTPClient HTTPClient} or by reading a {@link Titanium.Filesystem.File File}.</p>\n\n<p>Blobs are often used to store text or image data.\nThe <code>Blob</code> object includes a number of properties and methods specific to image blobs.</p>\n\n<p>Android supports an {@link Titanium.Blob#method-append append} method, but\notherwise blobs are immutable.</p>\n\n<p>The {@link Titanium.Utils} module provides several utility methods for working with\nblobs, including methods for converting between blobs and Base64-encoded strings,\nand methods for generating SHA-1 and SHA-256 hashes and MD5 digests from blob data.</p>\n\n<p>The {@link Titanium.Buffer Buffer} object can also contain binary data, and is\nmore easily mutable. Extracting blob data to a buffer is somewhat roundabout:</p>\n\n<pre><code>var blobStream = Ti.Stream.createStream({ source: myBlob, mode: Ti.Stream.MODE_READ });\nvar newBuffer = Ti.createBuffer({ length: myBlob.length });\nvar bytes = blobStream.read(newBuffer);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Creating a blob from a buffer is much easier:</p>\n\n<pre><code>var newBlob = myBuffer.toBlob();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>In both cases, the conversion involves copying the data from one object to another, so\nyou should be conscious of the amount of the data being copied.</p>"]},"private":null,"id":"class-Titanium.Blob","members":{"cfg":[],"property":[{"name":"apiName","tagname":"property","owner":"Titanium.Proxy","meta":{"readonly":true,"description":["<p>The value of this property is the fully qualified name of the API. For example, {@link Titanium.UI.Button Button}\nreturns <code>Ti.UI.Button</code>.</p>"],"platform":["android 3.2.0","iphone 3.2.0","ipad 3.2.0","windowsphone 4.1.0"]},"id":"property-apiName"},{"name":"bubbleParent","tagname":"property","owner":"Titanium.Proxy","meta":{"description":["<p>Some proxies (most commonly views) have a relationship to other proxies, often\nestablished by the add() method. For example, for a button added to a window, a\nclick event on the button would bubble up to the window. Other common parents are\ntable sections to their rows, table views to their sections, and scrollable views\nto their views. Set this property to false to disable the bubbling to the proxy's parent.</p>"],"platform":["android 3.0.0","iphone 3.0.0","ipad 3.0.0","windowsphone 4.1.0"]},"id":"property-bubbleParent"},{"name":"file","tagname":"property","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"readonly":true},"id":"property-file"},{"name":"height","tagname":"property","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"readonly":true,"description":["<p>If this blob doesn't represent an image, <code>height</code> is 0.</p>"]},"id":"property-height"},{"name":"length","tagname":"property","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"readonly":true},"id":"property-length"},{"name":"lifecycleContainer","tagname":"property","owner":"Titanium.Proxy","meta":{"description":["<p>If this property is set to a Window or TabGroup, then the corresponding Activity lifecycle event callbacks\nwill also be called on the proxy. Proxies that require the activity lifecycle will need this property set\nto the appropriate containing Window or TabGroup.</p>"],"platform":["android 3.6.0","windowsphone 4.1.0"]},"id":"property-lifecycleContainer"},{"name":"mimeType","tagname":"property","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"readonly":true},"id":"property-mimeType"},{"name":"nativePath","tagname":"property","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"readonly":true,"description":["<p>If this blob doesn't represent a file, the value of <code>nativePath</code> is <code>null</code>.</p>"]},"id":"property-nativePath"},{"name":"size","tagname":"property","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"readonly":true,"description":["<p>If this blob represents an image, this is the total number of pixels in the image.\nOtherwise it returns the number of bytes in the binary data.</p>"],"platform":["iphone 0.9","ipad 0.9","windowsphone 4.1.0"]},"id":"property-size"},{"name":"text","tagname":"property","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"readonly":true,"description":["<p>If this blob represents pure binary data, the value will be <code>null</code>.</p>"]},"id":"property-text"},{"name":"width","tagname":"property","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"readonly":true,"description":["<p>If this blob doesn't represent an image, <code>height</code> is 0.</p>"]},"id":"property-width"}],"method":[{"name":"addEventListener","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Proxy","meta":{},"id":"method-addEventListener"},{"name":"append","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"platform":["android 0.9","windowsphone 4.1.0"]},"id":"method-append"},{"name":"applyProperties","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Proxy","meta":{"description":["<p>Properties are supplied as a dictionary. Each key-value pair in the object is applied to the proxy such that\nmyproxy[key] = value.</p>"],"platform":["android 3.0.0","iphone 3.0.0","ipad 3.0.0","windowsphone 4.1.0"]},"id":"method-applyProperties"},{"name":"fireEvent","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Proxy","meta":{},"id":"method-fireEvent"},{"name":"getApiName","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Proxy","meta":{"platform":["android 3.2.0","iphone 3.2.0","ipad 3.2.0","windowsphone 4.1.0"]},"id":"method-getApiName"},{"name":"getBubbleParent","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Proxy","meta":{"platform":["android 3.0.0","iphone 3.0.0","ipad 3.0.0","windowsphone 4.1.0"]},"id":"method-getBubbleParent"},{"name":"getFile","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{},"id":"method-getFile"},{"name":"getHeight","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{},"id":"method-getHeight"},{"name":"getLength","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{},"id":"method-getLength"},{"name":"getLifecycleContainer","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Proxy","meta":{"platform":["android 3.6.0","windowsphone 4.1.0"]},"id":"method-getLifecycleContainer"},{"name":"getMimeType","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{},"id":"method-getMimeType"},{"name":"getNativePath","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{},"id":"method-getNativePath"},{"name":"getSize","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"platform":["iphone 0.9","ipad 0.9","windowsphone 4.1.0"]},"id":"method-getSize"},{"name":"getText","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{},"id":"method-getText"},{"name":"getWidth","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{},"id":"method-getWidth"},{"name":"imageAsCompressed","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"description":["<p>Returns the compressed image as a blob.</p>\n\n<p>If this blob doesn't represent an image, returns <code>null</code>.</p>"],"platform":["android 6.1.0","iphone 6.1.0","ipad 6.1.0"]},"id":"method-imageAsCompressed"},{"name":"imageAsCropped","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"description":["<p>Returns the cropped image as a blob.</p>\n\n<p>If this blob doesn't represent an image, returns <code>null</code>.</p>"],"platform":["android 3.0.0","iphone 0.9","ipad 0.9","windowsphone 4.1.0"]},"id":"method-imageAsCropped"},{"name":"imageAsResized","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"description":["<p>Returns the resized image as a blob.</p>\n\n<p>If this blob doesn't represent an image, returns <code>null</code>.</p>"],"platform":["android 3.0.0","iphone 0.9","ipad 0.9","windowsphone 4.1.0"]},"id":"method-imageAsResized"},{"name":"imageAsThumbnail","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"description":["<p>Returns the thumbnail image as a blob.</p>\n\n<p>If this blob doesn't represent an image, returns <code>null</code>.</p>"],"platform":["android 3.0.0","iphone 0.9","ipad 0.9","windowsphone 4.1.0"]},"id":"method-imageAsThumbnail"},{"name":"imageWithAlpha","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"description":["<p>Returns the new image as a blob, or <code>null</code> if this blob is not an image.</p>"],"platform":["android 3.0.0","iphone 0.9","ipad 0.9"]},"id":"method-imageWithAlpha"},{"name":"imageWithRoundedCorner","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"description":["<p>Returns the new image as a blob, or <code>null</code> if this blob is not an image.</p>"],"platform":["android 3.0.0","iphone 0.9","ipad 0.9"]},"id":"method-imageWithRoundedCorner"},{"name":"imageWithTransparentBorder","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{"description":["<p>Returns the new image as a blob, or <code>null</code> if this blob is not an image.</p>"],"platform":["android 3.0.0","iphone 0.9","ipad 0.9"]},"id":"method-imageWithTransparentBorder"},{"name":"removeEventListener","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Proxy","meta":{"description":["<p>Multiple listeners can be registered for the same event, so the\n<code>callback</code> parameter is used to determine which listener to remove.</p>\n\n<p>When adding a listener, you must save a reference to the callback function\nin order to remove the listener later:</p>\n\n<pre><code>var listener = function() { Ti.API.info(\"Event listener called.\"); }\nwindow.addEventListener('click', listener);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>To remove the listener, pass in a reference to the callback function:</p>\n\n<pre><code>window.removeEventListener('click', listener);\n</code></pre>"]},"id":"method-removeEventListener"},{"name":"setBubbleParent","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Proxy","meta":{"platform":["android 3.0.0","iphone 3.0.0","ipad 3.0.0","windowsphone 4.1.0"]},"id":"method-setBubbleParent"},{"name":"setLifecycleContainer","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Proxy","meta":{"platform":["android 3.6.0","windowsphone 4.1.0"]},"id":"method-setLifecycleContainer"},{"name":"toString","tagname":"method","owner":"Titanium.Blob","meta":{},"id":"method-toString"}],"event":[],"css_var":[],"css_mixin":[]},"linenr":72447,"files":[{"filename":"titanium.js","href":"titanium.html#Titanium-Blob"}],"html_meta":{"platform":"<ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>0.9</li><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>0.9</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>0.9</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul>","editurl":null,"description":"<p><p>A <code>Blob</code> represents a chunk of binary information, often obtained through\nan <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Network.HTTPClient\" rel=\"Titanium.Network.HTTPClient\" class=\"docClass\">HTTPClient</a> or by reading a <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Filesystem.File\" rel=\"Titanium.Filesystem.File\" class=\"docClass\">File</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Blobs are often used to store text or image data.\nThe <code>Blob</code> object includes a number of properties and methods specific to image blobs.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Android supports an <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-append\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob-method-append\" class=\"docClass\">append</a> method, but\notherwise blobs are immutable.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Utils\" rel=\"Titanium.Utils\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Utils</a> module provides several utility methods for working with\nblobs, including methods for converting between blobs and Base64-encoded strings,\nand methods for generating SHA-1 and SHA-256 hashes and MD5 digests from blob data.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Buffer\" rel=\"Titanium.Buffer\" class=\"docClass\">Buffer</a> object can also contain binary data, and is\nmore easily mutable. Extracting blob data to a buffer is somewhat roundabout:</p>\n\n\n\n\n<pre><code>var blobStream = Ti.Stream.createStream({ source: myBlob, mode: Ti.Stream.MODE_READ });\nvar newBuffer = Ti.createBuffer({ length: myBlob.length });\nvar bytes = blobStream.read(newBuffer);\n</code></pre>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Creating a blob from a buffer is much easier:</p>\n\n\n\n\n<pre><code>var newBlob = myBuffer.toBlob();\n</code></pre>\n\n\n\n\n<p>In both cases, the conversion involves copying the data from one object to another, so\nyou should be conscious of the amount of the data being copied.</p>\n\n</p>"},"statics":{"cfg":[],"property":[],"method":[],"event":[],"css_var":[],"css_mixin":[]},"component":false,"superclasses":["Titanium.Proxy","Titanium.Blob"],"subclasses":[],"mixedInto":[],"parentMixins":[],"html":"<div><div class='sidebar'><ul class=\"sidebar-platforms\"><li class='platform-android' title='Android since Titanium SDK 0.9'>Android 0.9</li><li class='platform-iphone' title='iPhone since Titanium SDK 0.9'>iPhone 0.9</li><li class='platform-ipad' title='iPad since Titanium SDK 0.9'>iPad 0.9</li><li class='platform-windowsphone' title='Windows Phone since Titanium SDK 4.1.0'>Windows Phone 4.1.0</li></ul></div><div class='hierarchy'><div class='classes'><div class='subclass'><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy' rel='Titanium.Proxy' class='docClass'>Titanium.Proxy</a></div><div class='subclass'> &gt; <strong>Titanium.Blob</strong></div></div></div><div class='doc-contents'><p>A container for binary data.</p>\n\n<p><p>A <code>Blob</code> represents a chunk of binary information, often obtained through\nan <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Network.HTTPClient\" rel=\"Titanium.Network.HTTPClient\" class=\"docClass\">HTTPClient</a> or by reading a <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Filesystem.File\" rel=\"Titanium.Filesystem.File\" class=\"docClass\">File</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Blobs are often used to store text or image data.\nThe <code>Blob</code> object includes a number of properties and methods specific to image blobs.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Android supports an <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-append\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob-method-append\" class=\"docClass\">append</a> method, but\notherwise blobs are immutable.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Utils\" rel=\"Titanium.Utils\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Utils</a> module provides several utility methods for working with\nblobs, including methods for converting between blobs and Base64-encoded strings,\nand methods for generating SHA-1 and SHA-256 hashes and MD5 digests from blob data.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Buffer\" rel=\"Titanium.Buffer\" class=\"docClass\">Buffer</a> object can also contain binary data, and is\nmore easily mutable. Extracting blob data to a buffer is somewhat roundabout:</p>\n\n\n\n\n<pre><code>var blobStream = Ti.Stream.createStream({ source: myBlob, mode: Ti.Stream.MODE_READ });\nvar newBuffer = Ti.createBuffer({ length: myBlob.length });\nvar bytes = blobStream.read(newBuffer);\n</code></pre>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Creating a blob from a buffer is much easier:</p>\n\n\n\n\n<pre><code>var newBlob = myBuffer.toBlob();\n</code></pre>\n\n\n\n\n<p>In both cases, the conversion involves copying the data from one object to another, so\nyou should be conscious of the amount of the data being copied.</p>\n\n</p><ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>0.9</li><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>0.9</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>0.9</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul></div><div class='members'><div class='members-section'><div class='definedBy'>Defined By</div><h3 class='members-title icon-property'>Properties</h3><div class='subsection'><div id='property-apiName' class='member first-child inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy' rel='Titanium.Proxy' class='defined-in docClass'>Titanium.Proxy</a></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-property-apiName' class='name not-expandable'>apiName</a><span> : String</span><strong class='readonly signature' >readonly</strong></div><div class='description'><div class='short'><p>The name of the API that this proxy corresponds to.</p>\n\n</div><div class='long'><p>The name of the API that this proxy corresponds to.</p>\n\n<p><p>The value of this property is the fully qualified name of the API. For example, <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Button\" rel=\"Titanium.UI.Button\" class=\"docClass\">Button</a>\nreturns <code>Ti.UI.Button</code>.</p>\n\n</p><ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>3.2.0</li><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>3.2.0</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>3.2.0</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul></div></div></div><div id='property-bubbleParent' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy' rel='Titanium.Proxy' class='defined-in docClass'>Titanium.Proxy</a></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-property-bubbleParent' class='name expandable'>bubbleParent</a><span> : Boolean</span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Indicates if the proxy will bubble an event to its parent. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Indicates if the proxy will bubble an event to its parent.</p>\n\n<p><p>Some proxies (most commonly views) have a relationship to other proxies, often\nestablished by the add() method. For example, for a button added to a window, a\nclick event on the button would bubble up to the window. Other common parents are\ntable sections to their rows, table views to their sections, and scrollable views\nto their views. Set this property to false to disable the bubbling to the proxy's parent.</p>\n\n</p><p>Default: true</p><ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul></div></div></div><div id='property-file' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-property-file' class='name not-expandable'>file</a><span> : <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Filesystem.File\" rel=\"Titanium.Filesystem.File\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Filesystem.File</a></span><strong class='readonly signature' >readonly</strong></div><div class='description'><div class='short'><p>File object represented by this blob, or <code>null</code> if this blob is not\nassociated with a file.</p>\n\n</div><div class='long'><p>File object represented by this blob, or <code>null</code> if this blob is not\nassociated with a file.</p>\n\n</div></div></div><div id='property-height' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-property-height' class='name not-expandable'>height</a><span> : Number</span><strong class='readonly signature' >readonly</strong></div><div class='description'><div class='short'><p>If this blob represents an image, this is the height of the image in pixels.</p>\n\n</div><div class='long'><p>If this blob represents an image, this is the height of the image in pixels.</p>\n\n<p><p>If this blob doesn't represent an image, <code>height</code> is 0.</p>\n\n</p></div></div></div><div id='property-length' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-property-length' class='name not-expandable'>length</a><span> : Number</span><strong class='readonly signature' >readonly</strong></div><div class='description'><div class='short'><p>Length of this blob in bytes.</p>\n\n</div><div class='long'><p>Length of this blob in bytes.</p>\n\n</div></div></div><div id='property-lifecycleContainer' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy' rel='Titanium.Proxy' class='defined-in docClass'>Titanium.Proxy</a></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-property-lifecycleContainer' class='name not-expandable'>lifecycleContainer</a><span> : <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Window\" rel=\"Titanium.UI.Window\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.UI.Window</a>/<a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.TabGroup\" rel=\"Titanium.UI.TabGroup\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.UI.TabGroup</a></span></div><div class='description'><div class='short'><p>The Window or TabGroup whose Activity lifecycle should be triggered on the proxy.</p>\n\n</div><div class='long'><p>The Window or TabGroup whose Activity lifecycle should be triggered on the proxy.</p>\n\n<p><p>If this property is set to a Window or TabGroup, then the corresponding Activity lifecycle event callbacks\nwill also be called on the proxy. Proxies that require the activity lifecycle will need this property set\nto the appropriate containing Window or TabGroup.</p>\n\n</p><ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>3.6.0</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul></div></div></div><div id='property-mimeType' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-property-mimeType' class='name not-expandable'>mimeType</a><span> : String</span><strong class='readonly signature' >readonly</strong></div><div class='description'><div class='short'><p>Mime type of the data in this blob.</p>\n\n</div><div class='long'><p>Mime type of the data in this blob.</p>\n\n</div></div></div><div id='property-nativePath' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-property-nativePath' class='name not-expandable'>nativePath</a><span> : String</span><strong class='readonly signature' >readonly</strong></div><div class='description'><div class='short'><p>If this blob represents a <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Filesystem.File\" rel=\"Titanium.Filesystem.File\" class=\"docClass\">File</a>, this is the file URL\nthat represents it.</p>\n\n</div><div class='long'><p>If this blob represents a <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Filesystem.File\" rel=\"Titanium.Filesystem.File\" class=\"docClass\">File</a>, this is the file URL\nthat represents it.</p>\n\n<p><p>If this blob doesn't represent a file, the value of <code>nativePath</code> is <code>null</code>.</p>\n\n</p></div></div></div><div id='property-size' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-property-size' class='name not-expandable'>size</a><span> : Number</span><strong class='readonly signature' >readonly</strong></div><div class='description'><div class='short'><p>Size of the blob in pixels (for image blobs) or bytes (for all other blobs).</p>\n\n</div><div class='long'><p>Size of the blob in pixels (for image blobs) or bytes (for all other blobs).</p>\n\n<p><p>If this blob represents an image, this is the total number of pixels in the image.\nOtherwise it returns the number of bytes in the binary data.</p>\n\n</p><ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>0.9</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>0.9</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul></div></div></div><div id='property-text' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-property-text' class='name not-expandable'>text</a><span> : String</span><strong class='readonly signature' >readonly</strong></div><div class='description'><div class='short'><p>UTF-8 string representation of the data in this blob.</p>\n\n</div><div class='long'><p>UTF-8 string representation of the data in this blob.</p>\n\n<p><p>If this blob represents pure binary data, the value will be <code>null</code>.</p>\n\n</p></div></div></div><div id='property-width' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-property-width' class='name not-expandable'>width</a><span> : Number</span><strong class='readonly signature' >readonly</strong></div><div class='description'><div class='short'><p>If this blob represents an image, this is the width of the image in pixels.</p>\n\n</div><div class='long'><p>If this blob represents an image, this is the width of the image in pixels.</p>\n\n<p><p>If this blob doesn't represent an image, <code>height</code> is 0.</p>\n\n</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class='members-section'><div class='definedBy'>Defined By</div><h3 class='members-title icon-method'>Methods</h3><div class='subsection'><div id='method-addEventListener' class='member first-child inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy' rel='Titanium.Proxy' class='defined-in docClass'>Titanium.Proxy</a></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-method-addEventListener' class='name expandable'>addEventListener</a>( <span class='pre'>name, callback</span> )</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Adds the specified callback as an event listener for the named event. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Adds the specified callback as an event listener for the named event.</p>\n\n<h3 class=\"pa\">Parameters</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>name</span> : String<div class='sub-desc'><p>Name of the event.</p>\n\n</div></li><li><span class='pre'>callback</span> : Callback&lt;Object&gt;<div class='sub-desc'><p>Callback function to invoke when the event is fired.</p>\n\n</div></li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>void</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-append' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-append' class='name expandable'>append</a>( <span class='pre'>blob</span> )</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Appends the data from another blob to this blob. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Appends the data from another blob to this blob.</p>\n\n<ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>0.9</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul><h3 class=\"pa\">Parameters</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>blob</span> : <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Blob</a><div class='sub-desc'><p>Blob to append to this blob.</p>\n\n</div></li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>void</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-applyProperties' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy' rel='Titanium.Proxy' class='defined-in docClass'>Titanium.Proxy</a></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-method-applyProperties' class='name expandable'>applyProperties</a>( <span class='pre'>props</span> )</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Applies the properties to the proxy. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Applies the properties to the proxy.</p>\n\n<p><p>Properties are supplied as a dictionary. Each key-value pair in the object is applied to the proxy such that\nmyproxy[key] = value.</p>\n\n</p><ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul><h3 class=\"pa\">Parameters</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>props</span> : <a href=\"#!/api/Dictionary\" rel=\"Dictionary\" class=\"docClass\">Dictionary</a><div class='sub-desc'><p>A dictionary of properties to apply.</p>\n\n</div></li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>void</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-fireEvent' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy' rel='Titanium.Proxy' class='defined-in docClass'>Titanium.Proxy</a></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-method-fireEvent' class='name expandable'>fireEvent</a>( <span class='pre'>name, event</span> )</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Fires a synthesized event to any registered listeners. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Fires a synthesized event to any registered listeners.</p>\n\n<h3 class=\"pa\">Parameters</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>name</span> : String<div class='sub-desc'><p>Name of the event.</p>\n\n</div></li><li><span class='pre'>event</span> : <a href=\"#!/api/Dictionary\" rel=\"Dictionary\" class=\"docClass\">Dictionary</a><div class='sub-desc'><p>A dictionary of keys and values to add to the <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Event\" rel=\"Titanium.Event\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Event</a> object sent to the listeners.</p>\n\n</div></li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>void</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-getApiName' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy' rel='Titanium.Proxy' class='defined-in docClass'>Titanium.Proxy</a></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-method-getApiName' class='name expandable'>getApiName</a>( <span class='pre'></span> ) : String</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Gets the value of the apiName property. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Gets the value of the <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-property-apiName\" rel=\"Titanium.Proxy-property-apiName\" class=\"docClass\">apiName</a> property.</p>\n\n<ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>3.2.0</li><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>3.2.0</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>3.2.0</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>String</span><div class='sub-desc'>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-getBubbleParent' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy' rel='Titanium.Proxy' class='defined-in docClass'>Titanium.Proxy</a></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-method-getBubbleParent' class='name expandable'>getBubbleParent</a>( <span class='pre'></span> ) : Boolean</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Gets the value of the bubbleParent property. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Gets the value of the <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-property-bubbleParent\" rel=\"Titanium.Proxy-property-bubbleParent\" class=\"docClass\">bubbleParent</a> property.</p>\n\n<ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>Boolean</span><div class='sub-desc'>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-getFile' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-getFile' class='name expandable'>getFile</a>( <span class='pre'></span> ) : <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Filesystem.File\" rel=\"Titanium.Filesystem.File\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Filesystem.File</a></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Gets the value of the file property. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Gets the value of the <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob-property-file\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob-property-file\" class=\"docClass\">file</a> property.</p>\n\n<h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'><a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Filesystem.File\" rel=\"Titanium.Filesystem.File\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Filesystem.File</a></span><div class='sub-desc'>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-getHeight' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-getHeight' class='name expandable'>getHeight</a>( <span class='pre'></span> ) : Number</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Gets the value of the height property. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Gets the value of the <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob-property-height\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob-property-height\" class=\"docClass\">height</a> property.</p>\n\n<h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>Number</span><div class='sub-desc'>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-getLength' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-getLength' class='name expandable'>getLength</a>( <span class='pre'></span> ) : Number</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Gets the value of the length property. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Gets the value of the <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob-property-length\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob-property-length\" class=\"docClass\">length</a> property.</p>\n\n<h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>Number</span><div class='sub-desc'>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-getLifecycleContainer' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy' rel='Titanium.Proxy' class='defined-in docClass'>Titanium.Proxy</a></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-method-getLifecycleContainer' class='name expandable'>getLifecycleContainer</a>( <span class='pre'></span> ) : <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Window\" rel=\"Titanium.UI.Window\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.UI.Window</a>/<a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.TabGroup\" rel=\"Titanium.UI.TabGroup\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.UI.TabGroup</a></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Gets the value of the lifecycleContainer property. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Gets the value of the <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-property-lifecycleContainer\" rel=\"Titanium.Proxy-property-lifecycleContainer\" class=\"docClass\">lifecycleContainer</a> property.</p>\n\n<ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>3.6.0</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'><a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Window\" rel=\"Titanium.UI.Window\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.UI.Window</a>/<a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.TabGroup\" rel=\"Titanium.UI.TabGroup\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.UI.TabGroup</a></span><div class='sub-desc'>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-getMimeType' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-getMimeType' class='name expandable'>getMimeType</a>( <span class='pre'></span> ) : String</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Gets the value of the mimeType property. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Gets the value of the <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob-property-mimeType\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob-property-mimeType\" class=\"docClass\">mimeType</a> property.</p>\n\n<h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>String</span><div class='sub-desc'>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-getNativePath' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-getNativePath' class='name expandable'>getNativePath</a>( <span class='pre'></span> ) : String</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Gets the value of the nativePath property. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Gets the value of the <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob-property-nativePath\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob-property-nativePath\" class=\"docClass\">nativePath</a> property.</p>\n\n<h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>String</span><div class='sub-desc'>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-getSize' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-getSize' class='name expandable'>getSize</a>( <span class='pre'></span> ) : Number</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Gets the value of the size property. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Gets the value of the <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob-property-size\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob-property-size\" class=\"docClass\">size</a> property.</p>\n\n<ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>0.9</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>0.9</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>Number</span><div class='sub-desc'>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-getText' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-getText' class='name expandable'>getText</a>( <span class='pre'></span> ) : String</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Gets the value of the text property. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Gets the value of the <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob-property-text\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob-property-text\" class=\"docClass\">text</a> property.</p>\n\n<h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>String</span><div class='sub-desc'>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-getWidth' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-getWidth' class='name expandable'>getWidth</a>( <span class='pre'></span> ) : Number</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Gets the value of the width property. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Gets the value of the <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob-property-width\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob-property-width\" class=\"docClass\">width</a> property.</p>\n\n<h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>Number</span><div class='sub-desc'>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-imageAsCompressed' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-imageAsCompressed' class='name expandable'>imageAsCompressed</a>( <span class='pre'>quality</span> ) : <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Blob</a></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Creates a new blob by compressing the underlying image to the specified quality. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Creates a new blob by compressing the underlying image to the specified quality.</p>\n\n<p><p>Returns the compressed image as a blob.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>If this blob doesn't represent an image, returns <code>null</code>.</p>\n\n</p><ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>6.1.0</li><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>6.1.0</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>6.1.0</li></ul><h3 class=\"pa\">Parameters</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>quality</span> : Number<div class='sub-desc'><p>Quality to compress this image to. From 0.0 (lowest quality) to 1.0 (highest quality).</p>\n\n</div></li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'><a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Blob</a></span><div class='sub-desc'><p>Compressed image as a blob.</p>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-imageAsCropped' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-imageAsCropped' class='name expandable'>imageAsCropped</a>( <span class='pre'>options</span> ) : <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Blob</a></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Creates a new blob by cropping the underlying image to the specified dimensions. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Creates a new blob by cropping the underlying image to the specified dimensions.</p>\n\n<p><p>Returns the cropped image as a blob.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>If this blob doesn't represent an image, returns <code>null</code>.</p>\n\n</p><ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>0.9</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>0.9</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul><h3 class=\"pa\">Parameters</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>options</span> : <a href=\"#!/api/Dictionary\" rel=\"Dictionary\" class=\"docClass\">Dictionary</a>&lt;<a href=\"#!/api/ImageAsCroppedDict\" rel=\"ImageAsCroppedDict\" class=\"docClass\">ImageAsCroppedDict</a>&gt;<div class='sub-desc'><p>Image cropping options.</p>\n\n</div></li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'><a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Blob</a></span><div class='sub-desc'><p>Cropped image as a blob.</p>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-imageAsResized' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-imageAsResized' class='name expandable'>imageAsResized</a>( <span class='pre'>width, height</span> ) : <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Blob</a></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Creates a new blob by resizing and scaling the underlying image to the specified dimensions. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Creates a new blob by resizing and scaling the underlying image to the specified dimensions.</p>\n\n<p><p>Returns the resized image as a blob.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>If this blob doesn't represent an image, returns <code>null</code>.</p>\n\n</p><ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>0.9</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>0.9</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul><h3 class=\"pa\">Parameters</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>width</span> : Number<div class='sub-desc'><p>Width to resize this image to.</p>\n\n</div></li><li><span class='pre'>height</span> : Number<div class='sub-desc'><p>Height to resize this image to.</p>\n\n</div></li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'><a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Blob</a></span><div class='sub-desc'><p>Resized image as a blob.</p>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-imageAsThumbnail' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-imageAsThumbnail' class='name expandable'>imageAsThumbnail</a>( <span class='pre'>size, [borderSize], [cornerRadius]</span> ) : <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Blob</a></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Returns a thumbnail version of the underlying image, optionally with a border and rounded corners. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Returns a thumbnail version of the underlying image, optionally with a border and rounded corners.</p>\n\n<p><p>Returns the thumbnail image as a blob.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>If this blob doesn't represent an image, returns <code>null</code>.</p>\n\n</p><ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>0.9</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>0.9</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul><h3 class=\"pa\">Parameters</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>size</span> : Number<div class='sub-desc'><p>Size of the thumbnail, in either width or height.</p>\n\n</div></li><li><span class='pre'>borderSize</span> : Number (optional)<div class='sub-desc'><p>Width of the thumbnail's border.</p>\n\n</div></li><li><span class='pre'>cornerRadius</span> : Number (optional)<div class='sub-desc'><p>Radius of the thumbnail's corners.</p>\n\n</div></li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'><a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Blob</a></span><div class='sub-desc'><p>The image thumbnail in a blob.</p>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-imageWithAlpha' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-imageWithAlpha' class='name expandable'>imageWithAlpha</a>( <span class='pre'></span> ) : <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Blob</a></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Returns a copy of the underlying image with an added alpha channel. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Returns a copy of the underlying image with an added alpha channel.</p>\n\n<p><p>Returns the new image as a blob, or <code>null</code> if this blob is not an image.</p>\n\n</p><ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>0.9</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>0.9</li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'><a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Blob</a></span><div class='sub-desc'><p>The image with an alpha channel in a blob, or <code>null</code> if this blob is not an image.</p>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-imageWithRoundedCorner' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-imageWithRoundedCorner' class='name expandable'>imageWithRoundedCorner</a>( <span class='pre'>cornerSize, [borderSize]</span> ) : <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Blob</a></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Returns a copy of the underlying image with rounded corners added. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Returns a copy of the underlying image with rounded corners added.</p>\n\n<p><p>Returns the new image as a blob, or <code>null</code> if this blob is not an image.</p>\n\n</p><ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>0.9</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>0.9</li></ul><h3 class=\"pa\">Parameters</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>cornerSize</span> : Number<div class='sub-desc'><p>Size of the rounded corners in pixels.</p>\n\n</div></li><li><span class='pre'>borderSize</span> : Number (optional)<div class='sub-desc'><p>Width of the border in pixels.</p>\n\n</div></li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'><a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Blob</a></span><div class='sub-desc'><p>Image with a rounded corner in a blob, or <code>null</code> if this blob is not an image.</p>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-imageWithTransparentBorder' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-imageWithTransparentBorder' class='name expandable'>imageWithTransparentBorder</a>( <span class='pre'>size</span> ) : <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Blob</a></div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Returns a copy of the underlying image with an added transparent border. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Returns a copy of the underlying image with an added transparent border.</p>\n\n<p><p>Returns the new image as a blob, or <code>null</code> if this blob is not an image.</p>\n\n</p><ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>0.9</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>0.9</li></ul><h3 class=\"pa\">Parameters</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>size</span> : Number<div class='sub-desc'><p>Width of the transparent border in pixels.</p>\n\n</div></li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'><a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Blob\" rel=\"Titanium.Blob\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.Blob</a></span><div class='sub-desc'><p>The image with a transparent border in a blob, or <code>null</code> if this blob is not an image.</p>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-removeEventListener' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy' rel='Titanium.Proxy' class='defined-in docClass'>Titanium.Proxy</a></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-method-removeEventListener' class='name expandable'>removeEventListener</a>( <span class='pre'>name, callback</span> )</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Removes the specified callback as an event listener for the named event. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Removes the specified callback as an event listener for the named event.</p>\n\n<p><p>Multiple listeners can be registered for the same event, so the\n<code>callback</code> parameter is used to determine which listener to remove.</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>When adding a listener, you must save a reference to the callback function\nin order to remove the listener later:</p>\n\n\n\n\n<pre><code>var listener = function() { Ti.API.info(\"Event listener called.\"); }\nwindow.addEventListener('click', listener);\n</code></pre>\n\n\n\n\n<p>To remove the listener, pass in a reference to the callback function:</p>\n\n\n\n\n<pre><code>window.removeEventListener('click', listener);\n</code></pre>\n\n</p><h3 class=\"pa\">Parameters</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>name</span> : String<div class='sub-desc'><p>Name of the event.</p>\n\n</div></li><li><span class='pre'>callback</span> : Callback&lt;Object&gt;<div class='sub-desc'><p>Callback function to remove. Must be the same function passed to <code>addEventListener</code>.</p>\n\n</div></li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>void</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-setBubbleParent' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy' rel='Titanium.Proxy' class='defined-in docClass'>Titanium.Proxy</a></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-method-setBubbleParent' class='name expandable'>setBubbleParent</a>( <span class='pre'>bubbleParent</span> )</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Sets the value of the bubbleParent property. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Sets the value of the <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-property-bubbleParent\" rel=\"Titanium.Proxy-property-bubbleParent\" class=\"docClass\">bubbleParent</a> property.</p>\n\n<ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-iphone'\n        title='iPhone'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-ipad'\n        title='iPad'>3.0.0</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul><h3 class=\"pa\">Parameters</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>bubbleParent</span> : Boolean<div class='sub-desc'><p>New value for the property.</p>\n\n</div></li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>void</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-setLifecycleContainer' class='member  inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy' rel='Titanium.Proxy' class='defined-in docClass'>Titanium.Proxy</a></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-method-setLifecycleContainer' class='name expandable'>setLifecycleContainer</a>( <span class='pre'>lifecycleContainer</span> )</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Sets the value of the lifecycleContainer property. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Sets the value of the <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.Proxy-property-lifecycleContainer\" rel=\"Titanium.Proxy-property-lifecycleContainer\" class=\"docClass\">lifecycleContainer</a> property.</p>\n\n<ul class='platforms'><li class='platform-android'\n        title='Android'>3.6.0</li><li class='platform-windowsphone'\n        title='Window Phone'>4.1.0</li></ul><h3 class=\"pa\">Parameters</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>lifecycleContainer</span> : <a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.Window\" rel=\"Titanium.UI.Window\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.UI.Window</a>/<a href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.TabGroup\" rel=\"Titanium.UI.TabGroup\" class=\"docClass\">Titanium.UI.TabGroup</a><div class='sub-desc'><p>New value for the property.</p>\n\n</div></li></ul><h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>void</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div id='method-toString' class='member  not-inherited'><a href='#' class='side expandable'><span>&nbsp;</span></a><div class='title'><div class='meta'><span class='defined-in' rel='Titanium.Blob'>Titanium.Blob</span></div><a href='#!/api/Titanium.Blob-method-toString' class='name expandable'>toString</a>( <span class='pre'></span> ) : String</div><div class='description'><div class='short'>Returns a string representation of this blob. ...</div><div class='long'><p>Returns a string representation of this blob.</p>\n\n<h3 class='pa'>Returns</h3><ul><li><span class='pre'>String</span><div class='sub-desc'>\n</div></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>"});